{"tid":749544,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪依家啲m記啲薯條都係裝到咁？","createTime":"2018-07-20T06:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T10:36:50.000Z","uid":146887,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f318de1105823f63240bcece32e319af6832faa0","tid":749544,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"口痕想食下shark shark薯條<br />\n諗住細薯個袋冇得出術 買細薯返屋企shark實冇事<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/141750_e5502f62637fe7f764bc10ab7525aff6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F141750_e5502f62637fe7f764bc10ab7525aff6.png&h=9d5251a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好再少啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做錯啲咩？"},{"pid":"c1d6dc72d67942b7edf20c8a74dda80998be5bcc","tid":749544,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"間m記班員工有份開架 <br />\n塞多d佢地會蝕到入肉"},{"pid":"8acec2981b4b55e87e848cf86e8d2011b8166402","tid":749544,"uid":166190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"裝得太多會比m記經理話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57593c212a1701f038c58dc8d687a113b65e895d","tid":749544,"uid":146887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/142504_8678eeec96410de7b6b7326ebbb6de8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F142504_8678eeec96410de7b6b7326ebbb6de8b.png&h=a85f72a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nshark完 真係兩啖食得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6bc